{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}我从来没见过他.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}l've never seen him before.{\r}

193
00:30:06,600 --> 00:30:09,070
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}主啊，无论你往哪里去...{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Wherever you go, Lord...{\r}

194
00:30:09,770 --> 00:30:13,470
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}...我都要跟随你.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}...l will follow.{\r}

195
00:30:16,140 --> 00:30:20,600
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}同你一起下狱，同去受死.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}To prison, even to death.{\r}

196
00:30:24,650 --> 00:30:27,120
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}我实在告诉你...{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Amen, l say to you...{\r}

197
00:30:29,720 --> 00:30:32,690
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}...今夜鸡叫以前...{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}...before the cock crows...{\r}

198
00:30:35,330 --> 00:30:38,260
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}...你要三次不认我.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}...three times you will deny me.{\r}

199
00:31:02,460 --> 00:31:03,790
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}伯多禄？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Peter?{\r}

200
00:31:19,640 --> 00:31:22,160
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}不要...我不配!{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}No, no...l am unworthy!{\r}

201
00:31:23,280 --> 00:31:26,770
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}我否认了他，母亲！{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}l have denied him, Mother!{\r}

202
00:31:27,880 --> 00:31:31,340
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}我有三次不敢认他.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Denied him three times.{\r}

203
00:31:43,760 --> 00:31:47,630
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}我们走！去处理这件事.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Let's go! You take care of it.{\r}

204
00:31:51,470 --> 00:31:54,670
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}让他过来.他是个没用的东西.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Let him pass. He's harmless.{\r}

205
00:31:56,680 --> 00:31:58,470
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}放了他!{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Release him !{\r}

206
00:32:00,210 --> 00:32:02,110
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}银钱还给你.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Take back the silver.{\r}

207
00:32:02,550 --> 00:32:03,980
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}拿去!{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Here!{\r}

208
00:32:06,350 --> 00:32:09,950
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}我出卖了无辜的血，我有罪了.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}l've sinned, betrayed innocent blood.{\r}

209
00:32:12,630 --> 00:32:16,990
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}把钱拿回去.这与我有什么关系！{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Take back your silver. l don't want it!{\r}

210
00:32:17,530 --> 00:32:22,490
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}如果你觉得你出卖了无辜的血，是你自己的事.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}lf you think you've betrayed innocent blood, that's your affair.{\r}

211
00:32:23,740 --> 00:32:25,700
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}拿着你的钱走吧.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Take your money and go.{\r}

212
00:32:27,540 --> 00:32:28,700
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}滚！{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Now go!{\r}

213
00:32:55,500 --> 00:32:57,200
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}你怎么了？没事吧？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}What's wrong? Are you all right?{\r}

214
00:32:58,040 --> 00:33:00,060
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}看他的嘴，让我们看看？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Look at his mouth. Hey, can we look at it?{\r}

215
00:33:00,440 --> 00:33:02,600
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}要不要我们帮忙？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}You need help? Can we help?{\r}

216
00:33:03,680 --> 00:33:05,340
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}他流血了！快看！血！{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}He's bleeding! Look! Blood!{\r}

217
00:33:08,210 --> 00:33:11,340
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}别烦我...{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Leave me alone...{\r}

218
00:33:12,350 --> 00:33:13,510
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}...你们这些小恶魔!{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}...you little satans!{\r}

219
00:33:14,650 --> 00:33:17,920
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}啊！诅咒，你被诅咒了？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Aha ! Cursing! Are you cursed?{\r}

220
00:33:18,190 --> 00:33:19,850
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}他被诅咒了{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}He's cursed!{\r}

221
00:33:20,160 --> 00:33:22,090
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}对 诅咒! 就在他身上 看呀!{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Yes, a curse! lt's inside him, look!{\r}

222
00:33:34,670 --> 00:33:37,730
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}小心 他体内像滚油煎熬!{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Watch out, it's like burning oil from his bones!{\r}

223
00:33:42,480 --> 00:33:46,280
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}走开! 别来碰我!{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Get away from me! Leave me alone!{\r}

224
00:38:04,680 --> 00:38:08,010
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}不要定这个加里肋亚人的罪.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Don't condemn this Galilean.{\r}

225
00:38:08,350 --> 00:38:09,710
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}他是圣洁者.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}He's holy.{\r}

226
00:38:10,380 --> 00:38:12,540
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}那样做只会替你自己惹来麻烦.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}You will only bring trouble on yourself.{\r}

227
00:38:12,890 --> 00:38:15,880
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}你知道我认为的麻烦是什么吗 克劳蒂亚？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Do you want to know my idea of trouble, Claudia?{\r}

228
00:38:16,290 --> 00:38:20,520
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}在这鬼地方和管理外面那些暴民.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}This stinking outpost, that filthy rabble out there.{\r}

229
00:39:04,370 --> 00:39:07,240
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}你们都是先拷打然后才审判？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Do you always punish your prisoners before they're judged?{\r}

230
00:39:07,610 --> 00:39:08,570
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}总督大人...{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Governor...{\r}

231
00:39:08,670 --> 00:39:11,230
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}你们对这人提出什么控告？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}What accusations do you bring against this man?{\r}

232
00:39:13,050 --> 00:39:14,310
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}这个...{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Well...{\r}

233
00:39:15,050 --> 00:39:18,980
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}如果这人不是作恶的，我们便不会把他交给你.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}lf he weren't a malefactor, we wouldn't have brought him before you.{\r}

234
00:39:19,420 --> 00:39:20,980
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}我不是问这个.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}That's not what l asked.{\r}

235
00:39:21,590 --> 00:39:23,920
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}你们为何不按照你们的法律审判他？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Why don't you judge him according to your own laws?{\r}

236
00:39:24,260 --> 00:39:27,990
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}大人，你知道我们是不许...{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Consul, you know it's unlawful for us...{\r}

237
00:39:28,530 --> 00:39:31,760
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}...处死任何人的.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}...to condemn any man to death.{\r}

238
00:39:32,570 --> 00:39:33,760
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}判死刑？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}To death?{\r}

239
00:39:34,130 --> 00:39:37,430
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}这个人究竟做了什么，要判他死刑？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}What has this man done to merit such a penalty?{\r}

240
00:39:37,700 --> 00:39:39,470
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}他不守安息日.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}He has violated our Sabbath, Consul.{\r}

241
00:39:42,070 --> 00:39:43,100
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}继续...{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Go on...{\r}

242
00:39:43,210 --> 00:39:45,040
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}他妖言惑众{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}He has seduced the people...{\r}

243
00:39:45,410 --> 00:39:48,850
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}...教坏人民，宣传邪说.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}...taught foul, disgusting doctrines.{\r}

244
00:39:51,020 --> 00:39:54,350
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}五天前，难道不是你们把他当先知迎进耶路撒冷？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}lsn't he the prophet you welcomed into Jerusalem only five days ago?{\r}

245
00:39:55,090 --> 00:39:59,510
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}现在却要杀他，谁能解释一下这疯狂的举动?{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}And now you want him dead? Can any of you explain this madness to me?{\r}

246
00:40:09,270 --> 00:40:10,740
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}总督大人 请听我说...{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Your Excellency, please...{\r}

247
00:40:12,610 --> 00:40:17,670
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}大司祭还没向你禀报他的重罪{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}So far the high priest hasn't told you this man's greatest crime.{\r}

248
00:40:18,680 --> 00:40:22,310
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}他是一群危险份子的领导{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}He has become the leader of a large and dangerous sect...{\r}

249
00:40:22,680 --> 00:40:25,480
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}...他们称呼他大卫的后裔{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}...who hail him as the Son of David!{\r}

250
00:40:26,950 --> 00:40:31,080
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}他自称是默西亚...{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}He claims that he is the Messiah...{\r}

251
00:40:31,560 --> 00:40:34,190
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}...天主预许的犹太人的国王.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}...the king promised to the Jews.{\r}

252
00:40:35,490 --> 00:40:40,450
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}他还阻止追随者给凯撒纳税.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}He has forbidden his followers to pay tribute to the emperor, Consul!{\r}

253
00:40:47,470 --> 00:40:48,940
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}带他上来！{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Bring him here!{\r}

254
00:41:21,070 --> 00:41:22,130
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}下去！{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Go!{\r}

255
00:41:28,110 --> 00:41:29,210
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}喝吧.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Drink.{\r}

256
00:41:42,530 --> 00:41:45,500
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}你是犹太人的君王吗？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Are you the king of the Jews?{\r}

257
00:41:48,000 --> 00:41:50,630
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}这话是你由自己说的？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Does this question come from you?{\r}

258
00:41:51,140 --> 00:41:56,100
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}或是别人论我而对你说的？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Or do you ask me this because others have told you that is what l am?{\r}

259
00:41:57,840 --> 00:42:00,870
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}我不是要问你这个？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Why would l ask you that?{\r}

260
00:42:01,650 --> 00:42:03,140
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}莫非我是犹太人？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Am l a Jew?{\r}

261
00:42:03,880 --> 00:42:08,840
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}你的民族和司祭长把你交付给我.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Your high priests, your own people delivered you up to me.{\r}

262
00:42:09,520 --> 00:42:11,180
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}他们要我处决你.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}They want me to have you executed.{\r}

263
00:42:11,560 --> 00:42:13,720
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}为什么，你作了什么？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Why? What have you done?{\r}

264
00:42:16,730 --> 00:42:18,530
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}你是不是王？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Are you a king?{\r}

265
00:42:22,600 --> 00:42:25,400
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}我的国不属于这世界.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}My kingdom is not of this world.{\r}

266
00:42:25,840 --> 00:42:27,470
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}假使我的国属于这世界...{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}lf it were...{\r}

267
00:42:27,740 --> 00:42:32,540
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}...我的臣民早已反抗了，使我不至于被交给犹太人？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}...do you think my followers would have let them hand me over?{\r}

268
00:42:34,010 --> 00:42:35,570
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}那么，你就是君王了？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Then you are a king?{\r}

269
00:42:38,050 --> 00:42:40,640
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}我为此而生.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}That is why l was born.{\r}

270
00:42:41,550 --> 00:42:44,350
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}为给真理作证.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}To give testimony to the truth.{\r}

271
00:42:45,120 --> 00:42:50,080
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}凡属于真理的，必听从我的声音.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}All men who hear the truth hear my voice.{\r}

272
00:42:52,060 --> 00:42:53,530
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}真理！{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Truth!{\r}

273
00:42:57,900 --> 00:43:00,100
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}什么是真理？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}What is truth?{\r}

274
00:43:26,170 --> 00:43:30,120
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}我已经问过了，我在这人身上查不出什么罪状来.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}l have questioned this prisoner, and l find no cause in him.{\r}

275
00:43:41,050 --> 00:43:42,600
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}他不是加里肋亚人吗？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}This man is a Galilean, is he not?{\r}

276
00:43:43,920 --> 00:43:45,080
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}是的.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}He is.{\r}

277
00:43:45,320 --> 00:43:47,580
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}那么他归黑落德王管.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Then he is King Herod's subject.{\r}

278
00:43:48,620 --> 00:43:50,210
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}让黑落德审判他.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Let Herod judge him.{\r}

279
00:43:50,560 --> 00:43:51,390
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}总督...{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Governor...{\r}

280
00:43:51,490 --> 00:43:52,890
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}把他交给黑落德.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Hand him over.{\r}

281
00:44:16,250 --> 00:44:17,940
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}纳匝肋人耶稣！{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Jesus of Nazareth!{\r}

282
00:44:18,580 --> 00:44:19,880
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}在哪里？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Where?{\r}

283
00:44:24,990 --> 00:44:26,420
