00:44:33,500 --> 00:44:35,020
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}这就是...{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}This...{\r}

285
00:44:36,570 --> 00:44:38,330
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}...纳匝肋人耶稣？{\r}
