287
00:44:51,020 --> 00:44:52,780
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}...叫死人复活？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Raise men from the dead?{\r}

288
00:45:09,800 --> 00:45:13,970
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}你的能力从哪来的？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Where do you get your power?{\r}

289
00:45:20,110 --> 00:45:25,070
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}预言中要降世的人就是你？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Are you the one whose birth was foretold?{\r}

290
00:45:31,790 --> 00:45:33,620
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}回答我！{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Answer me!{\r}

291
00:45:34,590 --> 00:45:36,030
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}你是不是君王？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Are you a king?{\r}

292
00:45:41,200 --> 00:45:42,830
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}那我算什么？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}How about me?{\r}

293
00:45:44,870 --> 00:45:47,570
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}行个神迹给我看好吗？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Will you work a little miracle for me?{\r}

294
00:46:03,920 --> 00:46:07,550
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}把这个傻子带走.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Take this stupid fool out of my sight.{\r}

295
00:46:08,060 --> 00:46:11,090
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}他没有罪，他只是疯了.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}He's not guilty of a crime, he's just crazy.{\r}

296
00:46:13,070 --> 00:46:16,330
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}给他傻子的待遇...{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Give him a fool's homage...{\r}

297
00:46:38,920 --> 00:46:40,760
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}克劳蒂亚，真理是什么？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}What is truth, Claudia?{\r}

298
00:46:41,430 --> 00:46:46,190
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}听到真理时,你能明白吗？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Do you hear it, recognize it when it is spoken?{\r}

299
00:46:46,970 --> 00:46:49,160
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}是的，我懂.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Yes, l do.{\r}

300
00:46:51,370 --> 00:46:52,770
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}你听不懂吗？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Don't you?{\r}

301
00:46:52,910 --> 00:46:54,530
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}如何明白？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}How?{\r}

302
00:46:55,270 --> 00:46:57,210
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}你能教我吗？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Can you tell me?{\r}

303
00:47:06,450 --> 00:47:11,290
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}你若听不懂真理，别人要教你也难.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}lf you will not hear the truth, no one can tell you.{\r}

304
00:47:13,090 --> 00:47:14,850
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}真理...{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Truth...{\r}

305
00:47:16,300 --> 00:47:19,530
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}你想知道我的真理吗 克劳蒂亚?{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Do you want to know what my truth is, Claudia?{\r}

306
00:47:20,670 --> 00:47:25,600
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}我在这鬼地方镇压叛乱已经11年了{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}l've been putting down rebellions in this rotten outpost for eleven years.{\r}

307
00:47:26,410 --> 00:47:28,370
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}要是我不判这人有罪...{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}lf l don't condemn this man...{\r}

308
00:47:28,740 --> 00:47:32,540
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}...盖法肯定会带头兴风作浪.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}...l know Caiphas will start a rebellion.{\r}

309
00:47:33,350 --> 00:47:36,780
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}我若判他有罪，他的信众又会闹事.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}lf l do condemn him, then his followers may.{\r}

310
00:47:37,780 --> 00:47:39,580
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}不论怎么做,都会有人流血.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Either way, there will be bloodshed.{\r}

311
00:47:40,120 --> 00:47:43,420
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}凯撒警告过我，克劳蒂亚，警告过两次.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Caesar has warned me, Claudia. Warned me twice.{\r}

312
00:47:44,320 --> 00:47:47,990
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}他说下次就该轮到我流血了.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}He swore that the next time the blood would be mine.{\r}

313
00:47:48,760 --> 00:47:50,420
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}这就是我的真理!{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}That is my truth!{\r}

314
00:47:55,330 --> 00:48:00,290
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}黑落德不肯判这人有罪.他们把他带了回来.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Herod refuses to condemn the man. They're bringing him back here.{\r}

315
00:48:00,940 --> 00:48:03,460
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}我们需要兵力增援.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}We're going to need reinforcements.{\r}

316
00:48:03,810 --> 00:48:06,070
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}我不想再引起任何暴动.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}l don't want to cause an uprising.{\r}

317
00:48:07,610 --> 00:48:09,580
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}暴动已经开始了.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}There is already an uprising.{\r}

318
00:48:35,240 --> 00:48:38,870
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}黑落德王找不出这人的罪状.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}King Herod found no cause in this man.{\r}

319
00:48:41,110 --> 00:48:43,880
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}我也一样.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Neither do l.{\r}

320
00:48:50,090 --> 00:48:53,250
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}来人，看住他们!{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Men! Attend to the crowd!{\r}

321
00:49:06,100 --> 00:49:07,470
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}肃静！{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Quiet!{\r}

322
00:49:07,940 --> 00:49:11,470
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}难道你们不尊敬我们的罗马总督?{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Have you no respect for our Roman procurator?{\r}

323
00:49:18,820 --> 00:49:23,150
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}你们知道，每年我该给你们释放一个犯人.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}As you know, every year l release a criminal back to you.{\r}

324
00:49:24,120 --> 00:49:27,290
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}我们现在有一个罪大恶极的杀人犯...{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}We are now holding a notorious murderer...{\r}

325
00:49:28,360 --> 00:49:29,790
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}...巴辣巴.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}...Barabbas.{\r}

326
00:49:46,580 --> 00:49:49,780
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}你们愿意我给你们释放哪一个？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Which of the two men would you have me release to you?{\r}

327
00:49:50,080 --> 00:49:51,980
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}杀人犯巴辣巴?{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}The murderer Barabbas?{\r}

328
00:49:52,250 --> 00:49:54,150
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}还是人称默西亚的耶稣？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Or Jesus, called the Messiah?{\r}

329
00:49:54,750 --> 00:49:58,950
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}他不是默西亚！是冒牌货！亵渎者！{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}He is not the Messiah! He is an imposter! A blasphemer!{\r}

330
00:50:00,130 --> 00:50:01,960
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}释放巴辣巴！{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Free Barabbas!{\r}

331
00:50:18,480 --> 00:50:23,440
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}我再问一次，这两个人你们要我释放哪一个？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Again l ask you: which of these two men should l release to you?{\r}

332
00:50:24,020 --> 00:50:26,310
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}释放巴辣巴！{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Free Barabbas!{\r}

333
00:50:42,270 --> 00:50:43,890
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}释放他.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Free him.{\r}

334
00:51:18,040 --> 00:51:21,470
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}那你们要我怎么处置纳匝肋人耶稣？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}What would you have me do with Jesus the Nazarene?{\r}

335
00:51:22,540 --> 00:51:24,370
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}钉他在十字架上!{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Have him crucified!{\r}

336
00:51:40,130 --> 00:51:41,150
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}不行!{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}No!{\r}

337
00:51:41,630 --> 00:51:43,250
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}我会鞭打他...{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}l will chastise him...{\r}

338
00:51:44,030 --> 00:51:45,390
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}...然后再放了他.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}...but then l will set him free.{\r}

339
00:51:50,140 --> 00:51:52,900
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}百夫长，给我重重地打.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}See to it that the punishment is severe, Abenader.{\r}

340
00:51:53,470 --> 00:51:56,640
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}但别让他们打死他.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}But don't let them kill the man.{\r}

341
00:53:18,420 --> 00:53:20,520
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}父啊，我的心已准备妥当...{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}My heart is ready, Father...{\r}

342
00:53:21,090 --> 00:53:23,060
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}...我的心已准备妥当.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}...my heart is ready.{\r}

343
00:57:47,030 --> 00:57:49,050
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}我儿...{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}My son...{\r}

344
00:57:50,730 --> 00:57:55,190
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}...你何时、何地、才能...{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}...when, where, how...{\r}

345
00:57:57,370 --> 00:58:01,100
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}...脱离这苦难？{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}...will you choose to be delivered of this?{\r}

346
01:02:22,770 --> 01:02:25,100
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}世界若恨你们...{\r}
