347
01:02:25,970 --> 01:02:30,930
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}...你们该知道，在你们以前，它已恨了我.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}...remember that it has hated me first.{\r}

348
01:02:36,680 --> 01:02:40,520
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}要记住，没有仆人大过主人的.{\r}
