349
01:02:41,950 --> 01:02:47,050
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}如果他们迫害了我，也要迫害你们.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}lf they persecuted me, they will persecute you.{\r}

350
01:02:49,030 --> 01:02:50,790
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}不要害怕.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}You must not be afraid.{\r}

351
01:02:51,630 --> 01:02:54,330
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}护慰者...{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}The Helper will come...{\r}

352
01:02:55,570 --> 01:02:59,830
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}...也就是真理之神会来...{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}...who reveals the truth about God...{\r}

353
01:03:02,810 --> 01:03:05,610
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}...由父而发出的.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}...and who comes from the Father.{\r}

354
01:03:12,520 --> 01:03:14,680
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}住手{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Stop!{\r}

355
01:03:16,850 --> 01:03:20,790
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}够了！让你们打他...{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Enough! Your orders were to punish this man...{\r}

356
01:03:24,100 --> 01:03:27,000
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}...但不是将他打死！{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}...not to scourge him to death!{\r}

357
01:03:33,600 --> 01:03:35,730
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}把他带走.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Take him away.{\r}

358
01:03:37,680 --> 01:03:39,010
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}快点！{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Get going!{\r}

359
01:03:48,690 --> 01:03:50,180
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}把他带走！{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Get him out of here!{\r}

360
01:05:21,910 --> 01:05:23,640
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}陛下...{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Your majesty...{\r}

361
01:05:24,180 --> 01:05:25,880
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}小心了.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Take care of it.{\r}

362
01:05:26,750 --> 01:05:28,380
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}一顶美丽的玫瑰花冠.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}A beautiful rose bush.{\r}

363
01:05:32,160 --> 01:05:35,350
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}看，犹太人的君王！{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Look at him...king of the worms!{\r}

364
01:05:36,490 --> 01:05:38,620
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}犹太人的君王，万岁！{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Hail, wormy king!{\r}

365
01:05:41,200 --> 01:05:43,390
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}这颜色最适合君王！{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}A color fit for a king!{\r}

366
01:07:59,770 --> 01:08:01,800
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}我们来朝拜你了.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}We're here to pay our respects.{\r}

367
01:08:04,140 --> 01:08:06,440
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}众兄弟们的领袖!{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}A leader for our brotherhood!{\r}

368
01:08:55,930 --> 01:08:57,620
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}看，这个人.{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Behold the man.{\r}

369
01:09:01,000 --> 01:09:03,090
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}钉他在十字架上！{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Crucify him !{\r}

370
01:09:13,810 --> 01:09:16,640
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}这还不够吗？看看他！{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}lsn't this enough? Look at him !{\r}

371
01:09:16,910 --> 01:09:18,640
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}钉他在十字架上！{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}Crucify him !{\r}

372
01:09:33,100 --> 01:09:34,720
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}要我把你们的君王钉在十字架上吗？{\r}
