373
01:09:36,370 --> 01:09:39,200
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}除了凯撒，我们没有君王！{\r}
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs9\shad0}We have no king but Caesar!{\r}

374
01:09:41,810 --> 01:09:43,670
{\fnFZDaHei-B02S\fs16\shad0}回答我.{\r}
